txt.en: Summoned forth by some vile incantation of the Witch-king of Angmar, dark reflections guard Tauressar, the Vandassar of Rhudaur, against all those who would hope to reclaim it.
Defeat many dark reflections in Tûr Fúar, the Drearspire.
